vel tuning needed in the top sector to achieve a phenomenologically\nacceptable vacuum state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Apr 2008 19:49:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Apr 2008 17:37:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-01-06"}
